		screen_text = "Greetings, visitor. It is highly unusual for a new face to show up here, at castle Cryhold. Whatever cause brought you here must have had you desperate. Both the Cave of Garrison and the Cave of Passage are overflowing with ice warriors. Our powers and resources are focused on preparing for the annual onslaught from the Cave of Garrison. The Cave of Passage leads into the kingdom, but is guarded heavily. What could you possibly seek here? I see, it's none of my business. Nevertheless. my supplies are available, if you can pay for them.";
